@startuml
title Match Lifecycle State Diagram

[*] --> Upcoming : Match Scheduled

state Upcoming {
  [*] --> PreMatch
  PreMatch --> SquadsDefined : Select Playing XI
  SquadsDefined --> TossCompleted : Conduct Toss
}

Upcoming --> Live : First Ball Bowled

state Live {
  [*] --> Innings1
  Innings1 --> InningsBreak : 1st Innings Complete\n(All out / Overs done)
  InningsBreak --> Innings2 : 2nd Innings Starts
  Innings2 --> CalculatingResult : Target Reached / All out / Overs done
}

Live --> Completed : Match Result Declared
Completed --> [*]
@enduml
